{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Phyllis Rodriguez: We are here today"},{"time":3000,"text":"because of the fact"},{"time":5000,"text":"that we have what most people consider"},{"time":7000,"text":"an unusual friendship."},{"time":9000,"text":"And it is."},{"time":11000,"text":"And yet, it feels natural to us now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":14000,"text":"I first learned"},{"time":16000,"text":"that my son had been in the World Trade Center"},{"time":20000,"text":"on the morning of September 11th, 2001."},{"time":24000,"text":"We didn't know"},{"time":26000,"text":"if he had perished yet"},{"time":28000,"text":"until 36 hours later."},{"time":33000,"text":"At the time,"},{"time":35000,"text":"we knew that it was political."},{"time":38000,"text":"We were afraid of what our country was going to do"},{"time":41000,"text":"in the name of our son --"},{"time":43000,"text":"my husband, Orlando, and I and our family."},{"time":46000,"text":"And when I saw it --"},{"time":48000,"text":"and yet, through the shock,"},{"time":50000,"text":"the terrible shock,"},{"time":52000,"text":"and the terrible explosion in our lives, literally,"},{"time":58000,"text":"we were not vengeful."},{"time":61000,"text":"And a couple of weeks later"},{"time":63000,"text":"when Zacarias Moussaoui was indicted"},{"time":66000,"text":"on six counts of conspiracy to commit terrorism,"},{"time":71000,"text":"and the U.S. government called for a death penalty"},{"time":74000,"text":"for him, if convicted,"},{"time":76000,"text":"my husband and I spoke out"},{"time":79000,"text":"in opposition to that, publicly."},{"time":82000,"text":"Through that"},{"time":84000,"text":"and through human rights groups,"},{"time":86000,"text":"we were brought together"},{"time":88000,"text":"with several other victims' families."}]},{"cues":[{"time":91000,"text":"When I saw Aicha in the media,"},{"time":94000,"text":"coming over when her son was indicted,"},{"time":97000,"text":"and I thought, \"What a brave woman."},{"time":100000,"text":"Someday I want to meet that woman when I'm stronger.\""},{"time":103000,"text":"I was still in deep grief;"},{"time":105000,"text":"I knew I didn't have the strength."},{"time":107000,"text":"I knew I would find her someday,"},{"time":109000,"text":"or we would find each other."},{"time":111000,"text":"Because, when people heard that my son was a victim,"},{"time":115000,"text":"I got immediate sympathy."},{"time":118000,"text":"But when people learned"},{"time":120000,"text":"what her son was accused of,"},{"time":122000,"text":"she didn't get that sympathy."},{"time":124000,"text":"But her suffering is equal to mine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":127000,"text":"So we met in November 2002,"},{"time":130000,"text":"and Aicha will now tell you"},{"time":133000,"text":"how that came about."}]},{"cues":[{"time":138000,"text":"(Translator) Aicha el-Wafi: Good afternoon, ladies and gentlemen."},{"time":144000,"text":"I am the mother of Zacarias Moussaoui."},{"time":153000,"text":"And I asked"},{"time":158000,"text":"the Organization of Human Rights"},{"time":160000,"text":"to put me in touch with the parents of the victims."},{"time":168000,"text":"So they introduced me"},{"time":171000,"text":"to five families."},{"time":177000,"text":"And I saw Phyllis, and I watched her."},{"time":182000,"text":"She was the only mother in the group."},{"time":187000,"text":"The others were brothers, sisters."},{"time":193000,"text":"And I saw in her eyes"},{"time":195000,"text":"that she was a mother, just like me."},{"time":199000,"text":"I suffered a lot as a mother."},{"time":206000,"text":"I was married when I was 14."},{"time":211000,"text":"I lost a child when I was 15,"},{"time":216000,"text":"a second child when I was 16."},{"time":222000,"text":"So the story with Zacarias was too much really."},{"time":228000,"text":"And I still suffer,"},{"time":232000,"text":"because my son"},{"time":234000,"text":"is like he's buried alive."},{"time":239000,"text":"I know she really cried for her son."},{"time":244000,"text":"But she knows where he is."},{"time":253000,"text":"My son, I don't know where he is."},{"time":255000,"text":"I don't know if he's alive. I don't know if he's tortured."},{"time":257000,"text":"I don't know what happened to him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":263000,"text":"So that's why I decided to tell my story,"},{"time":265000,"text":"so that my suffering is something positive for other women."},{"time":273000,"text":"For all the women, all the mothers that give life,"},{"time":280000,"text":"you can give back,"},{"time":282000,"text":"you can change."},{"time":284000,"text":"It's up to us women,"},{"time":287000,"text":"because we are women,"},{"time":290000,"text":"because we love our children."},{"time":298000,"text":"We must be hand-in-hand"},{"time":300000,"text":"and do something together."},{"time":304000,"text":"It's not against women,"},{"time":306000,"text":"it's for us, for us women,"},{"time":308000,"text":"for our children."},{"time":319000,"text":"I talk against violence, against terrorism."},{"time":322000,"text":"I go to schools"},{"time":324000,"text":"to talk to young, Muslim girls"},{"time":327000,"text":"so they don't accept to be married against their will very young."},{"time":343000,"text":"So if I can save one of the young girls,"},{"time":348000,"text":"and avoid that they get married and suffer as much as I did,"},{"time":351000,"text":"well this is something good."},{"time":355000,"text":"This is why I'm here in front of you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":357000,"text":"PR: I would like to say"},{"time":359000,"text":"that I have learned so much from Aicha,"},{"time":362000,"text":"starting with that day we had our very first meeting"},{"time":365000,"text":"with other family members --"},{"time":367000,"text":"which was a very private meeting with security,"},{"time":370000,"text":"because it was November 2002,"},{"time":373000,"text":"and, frankly, we were afraid of the super-patriotism of that time in the country --"},{"time":379000,"text":"those of us family members."},{"time":383000,"text":"But we were all so nervous."},{"time":386000,"text":"\"Why does she want to meet us?\""},{"time":389000,"text":"And then she was nervous."},{"time":391000,"text":"\"Why did we want to meet her?\""},{"time":393000,"text":"What did we want from each other?"},{"time":397000,"text":"Before we knew each others' names, or anything,"},{"time":400000,"text":"we had embraced and wept."},{"time":402000,"text":"Then we sat in a circle"},{"time":405000,"text":"with support, with help,"},{"time":407000,"text":"from people experienced in this kind of reconciliation."},{"time":411000,"text":"And Aicha started,"},{"time":413000,"text":"and she said,"},{"time":415000,"text":"\"I don't know if my son"},{"time":418000,"text":"is guilty or innocent,"},{"time":420000,"text":"but I want to tell you how sorry I am"},{"time":423000,"text":"for what happened to your families."},{"time":428000,"text":"I know what it is to suffer,"},{"time":431000,"text":"and I feel that if there is a crime,"},{"time":435000,"text":"a person should be tried fairly and punished.\""},{"time":440000,"text":"But she reached out to us in that way,"},{"time":444000,"text":"and it was, I'd like to say, it was an ice-breaker."},{"time":448000,"text":"And what happened then is we all told our stories,"},{"time":452000,"text":"and we all connected as human beings."},{"time":454000,"text":"By the end of the afternoon --"},{"time":456000,"text":"it was about three hours after lunch --"},{"time":460000,"text":"we'd felt as if we'd known each other forever."}]},{"cues":[{"time":462000,"text":"Now what I learned from her,"},{"time":464000,"text":"is a woman, not only who could be so generous"},{"time":467000,"text":"under these present circumstances"},{"time":469000,"text":"and what it was then,"},{"time":471000,"text":"and what was being done to her son,"},{"time":473000,"text":"but the life she's had."},{"time":475000,"text":"I never had met"},{"time":477000,"text":"someone with such a hard life,"},{"time":479000,"text":"from such a totally different culture and environment from my own."},{"time":484000,"text":"And I feel"},{"time":486000,"text":"that we have"},{"time":488000,"text":"a special connection,"},{"time":490000,"text":"which I value very much."},{"time":492000,"text":"And I think it's all about"},{"time":495000,"text":"being afraid of the other,"},{"time":497000,"text":"but making that step"},{"time":500000,"text":"and then realizing, \"Hey, this wasn't so hard."},{"time":503000,"text":"Who else can I meet that I don't know,"},{"time":505000,"text":"or that I'm so different from?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":509000,"text":"So, Aicha,"},{"time":511000,"text":"do you have a couple of words"},{"time":513000,"text":"for conclusion?"},{"time":515000,"text":"Because our time is up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":517000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":525000,"text":"(Translator) AW: I wanted to say"},{"time":527000,"text":"that we have to try to know other people, the other."},{"time":533000,"text":"You have to be generous,"},{"time":535000,"text":"and your hearts must be generous,"},{"time":537000,"text":"your mind must be generous."},{"time":540000,"text":"You must be tolerant."},{"time":545000,"text":"You have to fight against violence."},{"time":551000,"text":"And I hope that someday we'll all live together"},{"time":554000,"text":"in peace and respecting each other."},{"time":557000,"text":"This is what I wanted to say."}]},{"cues":[{"time":559000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}